    <item>
      <title>德国经济连续第二年萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/germany-sees-economy-contracting-for-second-consecutive-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府将今年的国内生产总值预测下调至收缩0.2%，这是欧洲最大经济体难以摆脱长期停滞状态的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/germany-sees-economy-contracting-for-second-consecutive-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利：4% 收益率有利于信用利差</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/morgan-stanley-s-sheets-4-yields-good-for-credit-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利企业信贷研究全球主管安德鲁·希茨 (Andrew Sheets) 认为，较高的收益率有利于信贷利差并给市场带来更多需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/morgan-stanley-s-sheets-4-yields-good-for-credit-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙希望法国媒体公司落户巴黎：综艺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/macron-prefers-french-media-companies-be-in-paris-variety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他更希望法国媒体公司在巴黎而不是其他地方上市，而法国维旺迪集团表示，作为拆分该企业集团计划的一部分，其倾向于将付费电视部门 Canal+ 在伦敦上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/macron-prefers-french-media-companies-be-in-paris-variety</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计 2024 年欧洲、中东和非洲地区新兴市场债券销售额将创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/jpmorgan-sees-record-emerging-market-bond-sales-for-emea-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通预计，尽管11月美国总统大选和中东紧张局势升级可能引发市场动荡，但欧洲、中东和非洲新兴市场的债券销售额今年年底仍将创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/jpmorgan-sees-record-emerging-market-bond-sales-for-emea-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗进军银行业的努力在 Atlas 首席执行官离职前遭遇阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/apollo-s-bet-to-take-on-banks-hit-snags-before-atlas-ceo-s-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这笔交易具备华尔街不可避免的权力转移的所有特征：新兴非银行贷款机构之王阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 抓住瑞士信贷集团 (Credit Suisse Group AG) 的弱点，抢占了这家瑞士公司最赚钱的业务之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/apollo-s-bet-to-take-on-banks-hit-snags-before-atlas-ceo-s-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
